    b"ids exactly as written.\x0d\x0a        - Each depth value must contain only created_af"
    b"ter, read_after, and\x0d\x0a          updated_after ISO 8601 timestamp strings.\x0d\x0a     "
    b"   - Use the current timestamp as the reference point for recency.\x0d\x0a        - Ch"
    b"oose each timestamp independently.\x0d\x0a        - Use older timestamps when older co"
    b"ntext may be useful.\x0d\x0a        - Use newer timestamps when recent context is enou"
    b"gh.\x0d\x0a        - Stop once the timestamp cutoffs look good enough for the request."
